        public void eat(Foods food)
        This method constructs eat of this pet.The pet eats foods,
        覆盖:
        eat 在类中 Pets
        参数:
        food - is one of the Foods.
        hungry - is increasing by the food. hungry must in range 0 to 100 if greater than 100, the hungry keep value equal to 100, if is favorite food of this pet, then double the hungry.
        fun - is increasing 10 by the food.
        toilet - is increasing 10 by the food.
        weight - is increasing 10 by the food.

      • paly

        public void paly(Toys toy)

        tried - is decreasing 10.
        hungry - is decreasing 10.
        toy - is one of the toys. when the fun increasing, the durability reduce 1.
